room_title: Escape room "The Morgue" by Rugged Xscape in Lafayette (IN)
room_description: A female patient named Rose disappeared from one of the active wards. They found her body in the abandoned room on the 13th floor. This ward had been used for sick, infectious patients, and had been closed down for years. Some say Rose wanders the building at night. Maintenance workers told us they saw a message scrawled on the wall: "I'm Not Crazy." Can you escape before your fate reaches you as well?
